# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.10.5] - 2025-10-30

### Added

- `deskew_tools`, tools for skew adjustments.
- `quel_config_ports` command.
- `modified_config`.
- Utility to measure SNR.
- Interface definition for delay measurement.
- A module to parse and use system configuration file.

### Changed

- Updated aiocoap version constraint to specify `<0.4.16`.
- Minor adjustments in packaging and tests.

### Removed

- Removed files for in-house tests.

## [0.10.4] - 2025-07-30

### Added

- `quel_filelock_manager`, a CLI command to handle file locks.
- An attribution file for third-party licenses.
- A workflow to build wheels and source distributions.

### Changed

- Relaxed version constraints of dependencies.
- Improved test environment.

### Removed

- Downloader for pre-built packages. Please use the PyPI repository or cloned source files instead. 
- Old scripts for building packages (release_utils).

### Fixed

- Flipped order in coefficients of CFIR and RFIRs.
- Inappropriate type hint in `read_counter()`.

## Older

You can see logs for older changes in ./UPDATE.md
